    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 2.5",
    "body" : "<p>The modulo operator is % (percent sign). To test for evenness or generally do modulo for a power of 2, you can also use &amp; (the and operator) like isEven = !( a &amp; 1 ).</p>\n"
