      "body" : "I my opinion the explicit if/else is easier on the eyes and faster to scan (would be even faster if opening brackets were on the same line as method signatures but after all that&#39;s personal preference). But we should not always go for &quot;shortest&quot; if it compromises readability (thinking of ternary operator-nesting)."
