    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 2.5",
    "body" : "<p>The code runs much faster without using modulo:</p>\n\n<pre><code>public boolean isEven(int a){\n    return ( (a &amp; 1) == 0 );\n}\n\npublic boolean isOdd(int a){\n    return ( (a &amp; 1) == 1 );\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
