    "body" : "<p>In <code>Java</code>, the <strong>mod</strong> operation can be performed as such:</p>\n\n<pre><code>Math.floorMod(a, b)\n</code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>Note:</strong>\nThe <strong>mod</strong> operation is different from the <strong>remainder</strong> operation. In <code>Java</code>, the <strong>remainder</strong> operation can be performed as such:</p>\n\n<pre><code>a % b\n</code></pre>\n"
