      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "Nice drawing. One other complexity: this doesn&#39;t take the 2^32 modularity of the <code>int</code> variable itself into account. The <code>floorMod</code> method does do that correctly (but you may need additional calculations if <code>n</code> is negative)."
